These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-1::.
There 5 different types of food: cauliflower, garlic, lettuce, pumpkin, radish
City: hannover, miami, edinburgh, marseilles, new-york
1. the person traveling to marseilles is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to marseilles is in the middle##1
3. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
4. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person traveling to edinburgh##2
6. the person eating radish is in the middle##1
7. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
8. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3    |    4    |    5    |
| Food          | garlic | cauliflower | radish | pumpkin | lettuce |
| City   | edinburgh  | new-york      | marseilles   | hannover     | miami    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-2::.
5 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, rat, hedgehog, dog
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, snowboarding, surfing, swimming, tennis
1. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the owner of the dog is in the middle##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
5. the person who's sport is badminton is between the owner of the rat and the person who's sport is swimming##2
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |    5    |
| Pet   | rat     | hedgehog       | dog    | ferret | guinea-pig   |
| Sport      | snowboarding | badminton | swimming | tennis      | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, filmmaking, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
There are 5 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, hot-chocolate, water, almond-milk
1. the person drinking water is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
8. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3      |     4      |      5      |
| Hobby         | card-games | magic-tricks | filmmaking | reading    | video-games |
| Beverage   | water     | milk        | hot-chocolate      | mirinda | almond-milk      |

