.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-4::.
5 different pets are kept: hamster, rabbit, horse, cat, mouse
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, martial-arts, satire, scientific, spy
1. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the mouse is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is between the person watching satire movies and the owner of the mouse##2
7. the person watching spy movies is the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |      5       |
| Pet         | hamster      | cat | horse | rabbit   | mouse  |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | spy    | satire        | adventure | martial-arts |

