.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: d&b, ambient, hip-hop, electronic, country
There are 5 different nationalities: australian, brazilian, canadian, egyptian, japanese
1. the fan of d&b is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of ambient is on the left of the australian##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the left of the japanese##1
4. the canadian is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
5. the japanese is on the far right##1
6. the fan of d&b is on the right of the egyptian##1
7. the brazilian is in an even position##4
8. the fan of hip-hop is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| Music-Genre      | country      | ambient | d&b   | electronic  | hip-hop  |
| Nationality   | canadian | egyptian | australian | brazilian | japanese |

