.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-6::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, lemonade, mirinda, tea
There are 5 different favourite colors: apricot, red, green, grey, yellow
1. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes red is between the person who likes yellow and the person drinking lemonade##2
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who likes red##1
5. the person who likes green is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person who likes green is in an even position##4
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
8. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |         2          |    3     |     4     |       5        |
| Beverage   | cola        | 7up                | mirinda  | lemonade  | tea            |
| Color        | apricot | yellow | red | green | grey |

