.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-7::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: punk, soul, salsa, hip-hop, gospel
The people have 5 different jobs:  doctor, electrician, firefighter, librarian, paramedic
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the electrician##3
2. the paramedic is on the left or right of the electrician##3
3. the fan of soul is in the middle##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of punk##1
5. the firefighter is in an odd position##4
6. the fan of punk is on the far right##1
7. the doctor is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
8. the paramedic is on the right of the electrician##1
9. the librarian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |      3      |     4     |       5       |
| Music-Genre   | gospel       | salsa   | soul    | hip-hop    | punk |
| Job        | firefighter | doctor | electrician | paramedic | librarian     |

