.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-8::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, lemonade, sprite, water
5 different games are played: backgammon, mah-jongg, go, domino, monopoly
1. the person playing go is the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person playing domino##1
3. the person drinking sprite is in an even position##4
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the person playing backgammon is between the person playing domino and the person playing monopoly##2
6. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
7. the person playing go is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3      |    4    |    5    |
| Beverage      | lemonade  | coffee       | juice      | sprite  | water   |
| Game   | monopoly | backgammon | domino | mah-jongg | go |

