2. the indonesian is the person who growsamaryllis##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is the indonesian##1
4. the indonesian is on the far right##1
5. the egyptian is the person who growslily##1
6. the indian is between the egyptian and the chinese##2
7. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the indian##1
8. the person who growsaconite is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Nationality   | thai | egyptian | indian     | chinese | indonesian |
| Flower           | aconite | lily     | daisy | sunflower    | amaryllis      |

