1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's sport is sailing is the alhambra-smoker##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4
6. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
7. the oliveros-smoker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2    |      3      |     4      |    5    |
| Cigar     | bluemaster | chaman | oliveros | alhambra | old-henry |
| Sport   | soccer | tennis | swimming    | sailing    | rowing  |

