1. the security-guard is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the firefighter is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
3. the firefighter is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is handball##2
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is tennis is the engineer##1
6. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
7. the entrepreneur is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |     4      |   5    |
| Job    | entrepreneur    | security-guard  | firefighter      | bartender     | engineer |
| Sport   | badminton | handball | skateboarding | ice-hockey | tennis |

