.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-12::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking, woodworking, fishing, puzzles
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, bus, car, skateboard, trike
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the trike is the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the person driving the trike is in the middle##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
5. the person driving the bus is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the trike and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
7. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
8. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |   3   |     4     |     5      |
| Hobby        | fishing | puzzles | camping  | woodworking | filmmaking     |
| Transport   | bus  | car     | trike | boat      | skateboard |

