6. the person traveling to london is between the australian and the person traveling to rome##2
7. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the mexican##3
8. the australian is on the left of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5     |
