.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-15::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: action, comedy, epic, martial-arts, mystery
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: soul, classical, trance, house, country
1. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
2. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
3. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of trance##1
4. the fan of trance is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
5. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
6. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
7. the fan of trance is in an odd position##4
8. the fan of house is in the middle##1
9. the fan of classical is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3       |    4     |    5    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | epic    | martial-arts | action   | mystery |
| Music-Genre   | country | classical | house    | soul | trance |

