.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-16::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, fuchsia, chestnut, yellow, azure
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: disco, pop, r&b, soul, trance
1. the person who likes yellow is the fan of soul##1
2. the fan of r&b is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes red is on the far left or far right##3
5. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
6. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3
7. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who likes azure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |    3     |    4     |   5    |
| Color           | red | azure | chestnut | yellow | fuchsia   |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | r&b            | disco    | soul     | trance |

