2. the victorian house is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person driving the taxi is in an odd position##4
4. the cape-cod house is between the gothic-revival house and the person driving the airplane##2
5. the person driving the bus is on the right of the craftsman house##1
6. the gothic-revival house is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
8. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |    3     |    4    |   5   |
