.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: disco, indie, punk, rock, soul
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, march, october, february, april
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the fan of soul##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the fan of soul##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in february##2
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the fan of soul##1
5. the fan of rock is in the middle##1
6. the person who's birthday is in april is the fan of disco##1
7. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |  3   |    4     |     5      |
| Music-Genre   | disco | punk      | rock | soul     | indie      |
| Birthday     | april | march | february | june | october |

 